        "newAxioms": 0,
        "sorries": 0
      },
      "tags": [
        "lean",
        "nbmellintools"
      ],
      "summary": "- The finite-approximation Nyman--Beurling criterion rules out zeta zeros in the right half of the critical strip. The left half is intentionally not claimed here: completing it requires a separately audited symmetry bridge."
    },
